CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 26, 1945, pg. 22, reads: "SO BIG - Master Leonard Tate Jr., son of Mr. and Mrs. Leonard Tate, celebrated his first birthday in a big way, recently. Present were, standing, left to right: Floyd Palmer, Rebecca Harris, Roland Noland, Westley Harris Jr., Duane Conners, Leonard Tate, Violet Copeland, Richard Collins, Roberta Harris, George Palmer Jr., and Gregory Harris Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group gathered around table with cake and napkins for first birthday party of Leonard Tate Jr., from left: Floyd Palmer, Rebecca Harris, Roland Noland, Westley Harris Jr., Duane Conners, Leonard Tate Jr., Violet Copeland, Richard Collins, Roberta Harris, George Palmer Jr., and Gregory Harris Jr.
